definitions.text:
@chia ly
* verb
-to disunite; to dissociate

[chia buồn] to offer one's sympathy/one's condolences to somebody; to condole with somebody 
 Xin thành thật chia buồn 
 Please accept my deepest sympathy; 
 Please accept my most sincere condolences; 
 With deepest sympathy; 
 With heartfelt condolences 
 Thư chia buồn 
 Letter of condolence/sympathy

@chia cắt
* verb
- To divide, to partition, to isolate

@chia rẽ
- To divide, to split the ranks of, to drive a wedge between
=gây chia rẽ+to sow division
